<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:14:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>外交部长表示台湾必须依靠自己的防御</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-must-rely-itself-defence-foreign-minister-says-2024-07-19/</link><description>台湾外交部长林家龙周五表示，随着中国加大军事压力，迫使这个民主岛屿接受其主权主张，台湾必须依靠自己进行防御。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:56:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-must-rely-itself-defence-foreign-minister-says-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国对美国丙酸产品启动反倾销税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-start-anti-dumping-duties-propionic-acid-products-us-2024-07-19/</link><description>中国商务部周五表示，自7月21日起，对原产于美国的丙酸产品实施反倾销税，实施期限为5年。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-start-anti-dumping-duties-propionic-acid-products-us-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因科技股溃败蔓延和全球不确定性而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-19/</link><description>尽管全球降息周期已经开始，但地缘政治格局和主要经济体的不确定性给投资者带来了不利因素，亚洲股市本周将以悲观收盘。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 02:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>由于交易员权衡美国利率，美元将维持每周涨幅，日元波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/dollar-set-eke-out-weekly-gain-traders-weigh-us-rates-yen-wobbles-2024-07-19/</link><description>由于美国劳动力和制造业数据让交易员思考美联储今年何时降息以及降息幅度，美元保持稳定，并有望在周五结束两周的跌势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 01:49:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/dollar-set-eke-out-weekly-gain-traders-weigh-us-rates-yen-wobbles-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国在瓦努阿图开设大使馆，中国竞争的最新举措</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-opens-embassy-vanuatu-latest-step-china-competition-2024-07-18/</link><description>美国周四在太平洋岛国瓦努阿图开设大使馆，这是美国与中国长期争夺亚太地区影响力的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 22:59:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-opens-embassy-vanuatu-latest-step-china-competition-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>随着经济增长放缓，中国顽固的储户无视消费诱因</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stubborn-savers-ignore-inducements-spend-growth-slows-2024-07-18/</link><description>尽管家庭存款放缓且银行大幅降息，但中国消费者支出未能对政府措施做出反应，这表明规避风险的居民更愿意偿还债务并购买理财产品。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 21:53:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-stubborn-savers-ignore-inducements-spend-growth-slows-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：科技风暴过后希望平静，日本消费者物价指数 (CPI) 着眼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-18/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 21:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>卢比奥称特朗普连任后将继续支持台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senate-republican-rubio-defends-trump-over-taiwan-remarks-2024-07-18/</link><description>入围美国总统竞选搭档唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)竞选搭档的共和党参议员马可·卢比奥(Marco Rubio)周四表示，他预计美国将在特朗普担任总统期间继续支持台湾。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 20:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senate-republican-rubio-defends-trump-over-taiwan-remarks-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国和加拿大外长周五在北京会晤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-canadian-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-friday-2024-07-18/</link><description>渥太华周四表示，加拿大外交部长梅兰妮·乔利将于周五在北京会见中国外交部长王毅，就双边关系和安全问题进行会谈。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:10:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-canadian-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-friday-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>随着古巴人采用电动自行车和汽车，哈瓦那的道路发生了变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/havanas-roads-change-cubans-adopt-electric-bikes-vehicles-2024-07-18/</link><description>哈瓦那以色彩缤纷的老式汽车而闻名，至今仍可以看到它们在街道上行驶，也是游客拍照的热门主题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 11:03:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/havanas-roads-change-cubans-adopt-electric-bikes-vehicles-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：台积电稳定芯片，欧洲央行和Netflix关注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-18/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国重申崇高的政策目标，但未提供实施细节</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pledges-industrial-modernisation-raft-other-reforms-2024-07-18/</link><description>中国领导人周四重申了广泛的经济政策目标，从工业现代化到扩大内需以及遏制债务和房地产行业风险，但没有详细说明实施步骤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:59:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pledges-industrial-modernisation-raft-other-reforms-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对欧盟猪肉发起反倾销调查，点名丹麦、荷兰、西班牙企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-singles-out-danish-dutch-spanish-firms-anti-dumping-probe-into-eu-pork-2024-07-18/</link><description>中国周四将丹麦皇冠公司以及荷兰和西班牙猪肉公司列为对欧盟猪肉进口进行反倾销调查的目标，北京方面加大了对欧盟限制其电动汽车出口的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-singles-out-danish-dutch-spanish-firms-anti-dumping-probe-into-eu-pork-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国共产党罢免最高机构中前外长、国防部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-removes-ex-foreign-defence-ministers-top-body-2024-07-18/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，周四，在中国共产党最大的最高决策机构会议上，中国共产党将前外交部长和国防部长秦刚和李尚福撤出中央委员会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:51:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-removes-ex-foreign-defence-ministers-top-body-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中美争端成焦点 芯片股波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asia-tech-stocks-skid-deepening-sino-us-chip-war-2024-07-18/</link><description>美国芯片股周四交易波动较大，费城半导体指数在周三暴跌后收高，英伟达和博通等几家重量级股的贡献最大。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asia-tech-stocks-skid-deepening-sino-us-chip-war-2024-07-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>